t data in the form of student and employer feedback indicate that the Program is meeting its stated objectives. The description of program operations, cost and fee structure, and implementation recommendations presented in this paper may be used as a guide for those faculty interested in implementing similar programs at their institutions. ', NULL, NULL, 'Robert F. Dombrowski and Kenneth J. Smith and Bob G. Wood', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.jaccedu.2012.12.003', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Journal of Accounting Education ', NULL, NULL, 'Education-practice gap', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', NULL, '84 - 106', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Bridging the education-practice divide: The Salisbury University auditing internship program ', NULL, 'http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0748575112001571', '31', '2013', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[vagner:6]', 'DombrowskiSmithWood2013', NULL, '1');
