l of Administrative Sciences / Revue Canadienne des Sciences de l'Administration', NULL, NULL, 'JEL Classification: M15, XBRL, XML, interorganizational system (IOS), case study', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', NULL, '125--135', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'John Wiley \& Sons, Ltd.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Co-operatively re-engineering a financial services information supply chain: A case study', NULL, 'http://dx.doi.org/10.1002/cjas.98', '26', '2009', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[vagner:6]', 'FahyFellerFinneganEtAl2009', NULL, '1');
