lication to accounting information systems research ', NULL, 'http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1467089511000200', '12', '2011', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[vagner:6]', 'Geerts2011', NULL, '1');
