n from unstructured data automatically. \{IC\} information analyst can rely on this method as an additional mean to identify and extract the commonly sought \{IC\} information from financial reports in a fast, systematic and reliable manner. ', NULL, NULL, 'Eric Tsui and W.M. Wang and Linlin Cai and C.F. Cheung and W.B. Lee', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.eswa.2013.08.029', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Expert Systems with Applications ', NULL, NULL, 'Intellectual capital management', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4, Part 1', NULL, '1315 - 1325', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Knowledge-based extraction of intellectual capital-related information from unstructured data ', NULL, 'http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0957417413006416', '41', '2014', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[vagner:6]', 'TsuiWangCaiEtAl2014a', NULL, '1');
